                            <comment id="15276130" author="aljoscha" created="Mon, 9 May 2016 08:56:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 The symlink thing should be fixed quickly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15276313" author="greghogan" created="Mon, 9 May 2016 12:41:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 with a consideration for &quot;start-scala-shell.sh&quot; -&amp;gt; &quot;flink-scala-shell&quot; since Java 9 is planned to include a Java REPL.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15696125" author="mxm" created="Fri, 25 Nov 2016 15:33:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 for the proposed renaming.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All scripts which import &lt;tt&gt;config.sh&lt;/tt&gt; automatically switch to the symlink resolved directory. So you can use &lt;tt&gt;pwd&lt;/tt&gt; or look it up in the &lt;tt&gt;SYMLINK_RESOLVED_BIN&lt;/tt&gt; variable.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
